Global Specimen Validity Test (SVT) Service Market Insights
Specimen Validity Test (SVT) Service Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Specimen Validity Test (SVT) Service Market Overview
The Specimen Validity Test (SVT) service market is valued at approximately USD 4.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2025 to 2030. The increasing need for workplace drug testing, along with the rising use of SVT in sports and legal cases, has accelerated demand for these services. The market's growth is also supported by heightened awareness regarding the importance of accurate specimen testing in healthcare, forensics, and research sectors. As regulations tighten, there is a significant push for advanced testing services that provide reliable and quick results.

